    <p>
Tsarin lissafi na dabaru (Logical Operators).
</p>
    <p>
Wato kamarsu "AND" da "OR".
</p>
    <p>
Hakan zai saka mamaki matukar ka san cewar zaka iya game tsarin da 
yake kunshe da tsarin Boolean sama da guda daya a lokaci daya sannan kuma duka a 
lissafi daya.
</p>
    <p>
To bari mu waiwayi misalinmu na cen baya a game din da Ali yana dawowa 
daga makaranta. A misalin an ce ana so Ali ya kauce matukar ya ga dutse 
ko ruwa a hanyarsa. To yaya za a yi a sanya wannan ka'idar a wajen kirkirar 
manhaja cewa matukar Ali ya ga dutse ko ruwa? To kuwa hakan zai iya 
yiwuwane ta hanyar amfani da wasu dabaru da ake kira 'tsarin lissafi na
dabaru'.
</p>
    <p>
Tsarin lissafi na dabaru yana iya game ka'idar da ake so amsarta ya 
Kasance E (TRUE) ko A'A (FALSE) sama da guda a lissafi guda. Kalmomin 
da ake amfani da su a wajen yin wadannan dabaru sun hada da su:AND, 
OR, da NOT.
</p>
    <p>
AND (SANNAN). 
</p>
    <p>
Wannan kalma ana amfani da itane a yayinda ake son aiwatar da wani 
umarni amma sai matukar amsar kowacce ka'ida ya zamanto E ne (TRUE) 
sai kuwa amsar umarninka ya zamanto E (TRUE) daga nan kuwa sai 
umarnin ya aiwatu. Amsar wannan lissafi zai zama E ne (TRUE) matukar 
kowacce ka'ida amsarsa ya zama E (TRUE) wato gaskiyane idan ba haka 
ba kuwa amsar lissafin zai zamanto A'A (FALSE) wato karya (FALSE). 
</p>
    <p>
Jadawali mai lamba 4-2 yana dauke da misalin yadda za'ayi amfani da 
Kalmar ta AND. 
</p>
    <p>
// Insert Table //
</p>
    <p>


NOT (MUSANYA).
</p>
    <p>
Shi kuwa wannan kalmar ana amfani da itane domin juya ko cenza amsar 
lissafin boolean zuwa dan uwansa. Wato yayi musanyar amsar da aka 
saka a wata ka'idar zuwa wata amsar. Misali, yayin da aka samu amsar E 
ne (TRUE) a ka'ida to kuwa amarka zai zama A'A (FALSE) idan kuwa A'A 
ne (FALSE) zai juya shi zuwa E ne (TRUE). Wannan kalmar ana amfani da 
itane a ka'idar daya kawai sabanin sauran kalmomin na AND da OR.
</p>
    <p>
Jadawali mai lamba 4-4 na dauke da misalinh akan.
</p>
    <p>
// Insert Table //
</p>
    <p>

Idan muka koma misalinmu dai na baya wato na Ali idan ya ga dutse ko 
ruwa a hanyarsa to ya kauce masa, to anan kalmar da ya kamata ayi 
amfani da shi domin zayyana wannan umarnin shine kalmar 'OR' (KO). 
Saboda anan amsarmu E ne (TRUE) matukar Ali yaga dutse 
ko ruwa a hanyarsa. Amsar umarninmu zai zama E ne (TRUE) matukar sai 
idan daya daga ka'idar da muka bayana ko ka'idojin biyun dukkanninsu suka 
zama E (TRUE). Domin kuwa hakan shi muke bukata domin samun 
amsarmu ta karshe wadda da shine manhaja ke aiwatarda wani umarni ko 
aiki.
</p>
    <p>
Misalina 1: 
</p>
    <p>
Ga misalin yadda za'a tsara umarnin da kuma ka'idojin a saukake 
</p>
    <p>
Asukake:
</p>
    <p>
Idan (Ali ya ga dutse KO Ali yaga ruwa)
To ya kauce musu.
Shikenan.
</p>
    <p>
Misalina 2:
</p>
    <p>
Za'a iya zayyana umarni masu matukar tsauri a wajen tsara umarnin.
</p>
    <p>
Asaukake:
</p>
    <p>
Idan (ana ruwan sama KO iska SANNAN koma taga a bude yake)
rufe tagar.
Shikenan.
</p>
    <p>

Fa'ida.
</p>
    <p>
Kada a manta, ma'anar wadann a nahausance sune kamar haka:
</p>
    <p>
AND shine SANNAN.
</p>
    <p>
OR shine KO.
</p>
    <p>
NOT shine MUSANYA. 
</p>
    <p>

IF ELSE (Tsarin auna zabi sama da guda).
</p>
    <p>
A cen baya mun danyi bayanai game da tsarin da ake kira 'decision
structure' wato tsari  zaba da yake zabar umarni bisa ga ka'idar da aka 
samar masa sannan zai aiwatar da umarnin ne muddin amsar ya zama E 
ne (TRUE). To me zai faru muddin dukkan amsoshin ka'idojin ka suka zama 
A'A ne (FALSE)? Anan sai muce babu wani umarni da zai aiwatar. Kamar dai a wancen misalin namu na Ali munce, idan Ali ya ga dutse ko ruwa to ya kauce masa to kuwa matukar bai ga dutse ko ruwa a hanyarsa ba zai ci gaba da tafiyarsane har zuwa gida. To matsalar 
Ita ce me zai faru idan ya ga wani abu ba dutse ko ruwa ba? To fa shine sai 
ayi amfani da tsarin IF ELSE (wato tsarin auna zabi sama da guda daya). 
</p>
    <p>
Misali.
</p>
    <p>
Musapha yana fadawa abokinsa Umar cewa ya saya masa wani kyauta a 
bulaguron da yayi. Sai kuwa Mustapha ya ba wa Umar kyautar wadda 
riguna ne guda biyu, daya nashi dayan kuma na dan uwan shi. Umar yana 
da yan uwa guda biyu, kaninsa da kuma yayansa wato wan sa. Sai Umar ya 
kaddara cewa idan daya daga rigunannan biyu yayi masa kadan ko yayi dai-
dai da shi to zai ba wa kaninsa ne amma idan yayi masa yawa zai ba wa
wansa ne.
</p>
    <p>
To yanzu a wannan yanayin dolene sai an samu tsarin da zai auna 
dukkannin ka'idojin nan biyu wato shin rigar tayi masa dai-dai ko ta masa 
karamine ko kuma dai ta masa girma? Domin samun amsar hakan ga 
misali kamar haka:
</p>
    <p>
Asaukake:
</p>
    <p>
Umar an basa kyautar riga.
</p>
    <p>
Idan (rigar yayi masa girma)
Ya ba wa yayansa.
Idan kuwa ba haka ba.
Ya ba wa kaninsa.
Shikenan.
</p>
    <p>

A wannan yanayin da ya gabata, koda rigar bata yi masa girma ba to 
dolene ace tayi masa dai-dai ko tayi masa kadan. Saboda dolene sai ya 
karanta daya daga wadannan ka'idoji da suka gabata domin bada amsa E 
(TRUE) ko kuma A'A (FALSE).
</p>
    <p>
Kenan, idan aka saka cewar rigar tayi masa girma to za a ba wa yayansa 
idan ba haka ba kuwa za a ba wa kaninsa.
</p>
    <p>
NESTING.
</p>
    <p>
Kafin mu rufe wannan babi za mu bayyana wani muhimmin tsari mai suna 'NESTING' wato tsarine mai shigar da wani ka'ida da umarni cikin wani. 
</p>
    <p>
'Nesting' yana nufin wani tsarine da yake bada damar sanya wasu kananan 
ka'idoji tare da umarni cikin wasu ko wani umarnin.
</p>
    <p>
A misalin mu da ya gabatana Ali, mun ga yadda aka sanya tsarii zaba 
cikin tsari mai bi daki-daki (wato 'decision' cikin 'sequence'). To wannan 
dabaran da akayi za a iya cewa anyi 'Nesting' din tsari zaba 
cikin tsari mai bi daki-daki. Hakama za a iya sanya tsari zaba cikin wani
tsarin zaban.
</p>
    <p>
A wasu babika masu zuwa, zamu yi dubi akan wannan batu in Allah ya
yarda.
</p>
